    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"//www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/VkZekcCRGao\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Administrators when first accessing their project on <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0041be; text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;\" target=\"_blank\">Customer Portal</a> are presented with the activation form for Liferay SaaS. If this step was skipped, please navigate to the left sidebar navigation, expand Activation and select </span><strong><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Liferay SaaS</span></strong><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">.&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" data-fileentryid=\"26207897\" src=\"/documents/d/customer-portal/screenshot-2025-10-02-121738\" /></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\"></span><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Upon selecting Liferay SaaS, you will see the current status of your activation form. If it has not been completed yet, the status will display </span><strong><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Not Activated.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"190\" src=\"https://support.liferay.com/documents/d/customer-portal/25029937603981-plan-and-usage\" width=\"563\" /></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\"></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Please click the link labeled as </span><strong><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Finish Activation </span></strong><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">and fill out the required information:&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Project ID (Note: This Project ID cannot be changed.)&nbsp;</span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Primary Region</span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Project Admin’s First and Last Name</span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Project Admin’s Email Address</span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Appoint your Critical Incident Contact(s) , Privacy Breach Contact(s), and Security Breach Contact(s)</span>\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Select at least one contact for each from your current team members list</span>\n\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t<li><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">For more details, see </span><a href=\"/w/how-do-i-manage-my-incident-contacts\"><span style=\"color: #0b5fff;\">How do I Manage my Incident Contacts?</span></a></li>\n\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Once the form is submitted, your information will be sent to our Liferay team for processing and the Activation Status will change to </span><strong><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">In Progress.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Activation will be completed within 1-3 business days and Administrators will be notified via email. Your Activation Status will then change to </span><strong><span style=\"color: #2a303e;\">Active.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>"
      },
